| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3374 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7c8e08be-03c2-5502-b9d6-d18ad3a40627"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
